node.text: Thank you to everyone for all the Dam Good Times we have had over these past 8 years. Normally we’d invite all of you to our anniversary party, and boogie the night away, but due to the current circumstances we had to switch it up this year. To everyone that purchased our beer boxes before they sold out, CHEERS! We hope you are enjoying the selection of beers we sent out to you. If you didn't get a chance to grab a box, stop by any of our locations to pick up some beer to-go or dine in and have a meal and pint with us. node.text:
Our fans guessed correct! We’re releasing our 8th collaboration with Deftones, Ceremony DDH Hazy IPA. This brew takes an easy drinking Hazy IPA and pushes the limits of our dry-hopping regiment- doubling down on the juicy and tropical hop varietals. 
 
If you’re local try it on draft or pick up a 4-pack at one of the following Belching Beaver locations today, North Park tasting room, Oceanside tasting room or Pub980. We want to get this into everyone’s hands, please note it is limit (2) 4-packs per person. For our fans in other cities order online today (starting at 11:30 am) at belchingbeaver.com or check our brew finder as it rolls out through our distribution channels in the coming weeks. 
 
We’re excited about this Hazy IPA and we can’t wait for you to try it! 
 
Key facts
Stats: 6.5% ABV, 30 IBUs
Hops: Citra, Galaxy
Beer style: Double Dry Hopped Hazy IPA 
U.S. availability: AZ, CA, CO, HI, ID, NE, NV, MN, OR, TX, WA, WI

🚨 FRIDAY RELEASE! 🚨 
Island Sunshine - Kettle Sour with Peach and Guava, 5.5% ABV

We created Island Sunshine with the Summer months in mind and brewed something fruit-forward and refreshing. The peach and guava in this beer gives it lots of tropical notes and balances out the tart flavors from the souring process. Enjoy this beer by the pool, with friends at a BBQ or at any Summer activity in the sun. 
Available this Friday at: @belchingbeaverpub980
